# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t,

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t

  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]

  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )

    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )
            
                       
                in (t

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )
            
                       
                in (t::acc

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )
            
                       
                in (t::acc)

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )
            
                       
                in (t::acc)@t

type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )
            
                       
                in (t::acc)@todo

type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list

let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then

                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )
            
                       
                in (t::acc)@todos

    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )
            
                       
                in (t::acc)@todos e

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )
            
                       
                in (t::acc)@todos else

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->

    fun idx, todos ->

let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )
            
                       
                in (t::acc)@todos else acc

type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2

  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->

    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)

  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer

  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )
            
                       
                in (t::acc)@todos else acc

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )
            
                       
                in (t::acc)@todos else acc

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )
            
                       
                in (t::acc)@todos else acc 
    
    
    in

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )
            
                       
                in (t::acc)@todos else acc 
    
    
    in   go(

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )
            
                       
                in (t::acc)@todos else acc 
    
    
    in   go(0

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )
            
                       
                in (t::acc)@todos else acc 
    
    
    in   go(0, todos

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )
            
                       
                in (t::acc)@todos else acc 
    
    
    in   go(0, todos

# A todo has a description and a status #
type Todo = (String, Bool) in

# A description input buffer and a todo list #
type Model = (String, [Todo]) in

type Action =
  + AddTodo
  + RemoveTodo(Int)
  + ToggleTodo(Int)
  + UpdateBuffer(String)
in

let Bool.eq: (Bool, Bool) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.init: Model = ("", []) in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )
            
                       
                in (t::acc)@todos else acc 
    
    
    in   go(0, todos

  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer

  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )
            
                       
                in (t::acc)@todos else acc 
    
    
    in   go(0, todos    )

  fun (b1, b2) -> if b1 then b2 else !b2
in

let Todo.eq: (Todo, Todo) -> Bool =
  fun (d1, s1), (d2, s2) ->
    d1 $== d2 && Bool.eq(s1, s2)
in

let todo_list_eq: ([Todo], [Todo]) -> Bool =
    fun xs, ys ->
    case xs, ys
    | [], [] => true
    | x::xs, y::ys => Todo.eq(x, y) && todo_list_eq(xs, ys)
    | _ => false end
in

let Model.eq: (Model, Model) -> Bool =
  fun (b1, ts1), (b2, ts2) ->
    b1 $== b2 && todo_list_eq(ts1, ts2)
in

let Model.get_buffer: Model -> String =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> buffer
in

let Model.get_todo_list: Model -> [Todo] =
  fun buffer, todo_list -> todo_list
in

# Toggle a todo item by its index #
let toggle: (Int, [Todo]) -> [Todo]=
    fun idx, todos ->
    let go: (Int, Todo, [Todo] ) -> [Todo] = 
        fun i, t, acc ->
            if i        < idx then t::acc
            else if i == idx then (t         :: acc) 
            else if i < List.length(todos) then
                let td = List.tl(todos) in
                let td_hd = List.tl(td) in
                let td_tl = List.rev(List.init(i, fun i -> List.rev(td) @ [Todo.eq(t, t) ]) )
            
                       
                in (t::acc)@todos else acc 
    
    
    in   go(0, todos    ) 
in
